:136281,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-11T23:27:13.000Z","msg":"唔好執啦 人地好地地生活緊 想養貓 不如去領養 果d隻比人類照顧過 冇得番大自然啦 同埋佢地有打針 對你都係一件好事"},{"pid":"c4c047abd2085547e2a15c87fe50dd9cf5a3baeb","tid":660430,"uid":828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-11T23:29:17.000Z","msg":"點解我執返黎嘅貓咁曳<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n一係就咬我 一係就整跌晒d嘢<br />\n你地係點教貓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}